## âš™ï¸ Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/finpilot-app.git
cd finpilot-app
npm install
cp .env.example .env.local
npm run dev
```

Set up your `.env.local` file with your Supabase / OpenAI / Web3 credentials.

